<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns dewchte ein notdurft sein, daz wir von
                        den <expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns von disen lewffen etwas
                                <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>unt<ex>er</ex>redt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und
                            <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> czü uns <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wöllet, daz die <app><note><q type="date">auf den montag cze nacht <add>nu</add> nach sant Andres tag</q>31.11.1410</note></app>
                        bey uns czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> sey, daz man sich des morgens
                        <app><note><q type="date">auf den eritag</q>01.12.1410</note></app> von den lewffen <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>rede</expan>; und
                                <expan>desgleich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>Weiss<ex>emburg</ex></expan> auch
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Kath<ex>er</ex>ine</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
